OL,3,CAlternative A5 Alliance says new dual
OL,4,Ccarriageway 'irresponsible' use of
OL,5,Cmoney
OL,7,FA group behind previous legal
OL,8,Fchallenges to the A5 upgrade has said
OL,9,Fthe proposed new dual carriageway is
OL,10,Fan "irresponsible use of public money."
OL,12,FA member of the Alternative A5
OL,13,FAlliance told UTV plans for a new A5
OL,14,Fdual carriageway linking Aughnacloy
OL,15,Fwith Newbuildings outside Londonderry
OL,16,Fare a "vanity project."
OL,18,FThe comments come after the
OL,19,FInfrastructure Minister said he will
OL,20,Fbe recommending that the planned
OL,21,Fupgrade of the A5 road should proceed.
