OL,3,CAlternative A5 Alliance says new dual
OL,4,Ccarriageway 'irresponsible' use of
OL,5,Cmoney
OL,7,FThere have been more than 50 deaths on
OL,8,Fthe road, which links Londonderry with
OL,9,FAughnacloy in Co Tyrone, since 2006.
OL,11,FPlans for the scheme were first
OL,12,Fannounced in 2007 but it has been held
OL,13,Fup by legal challenges and uncertainty
OL,14,Fover funding.
OL,16,FA member of the Alternative A5
OL,17,FAlliance refused to rule out the
OL,18,Fpotential for further legal challenges
OL,19,F- instead, they said they would be
OL,20,Fwaiting to see the full report once it
OL,21,Fis published.
