OL,3,CAlternative A5 Alliance says new dual
OL,4,Ccarriageway 'irresponsible' use of
OL,5,Cmoney
OL,7,FThe group is advocating for an
OL,8,Falternative to the dual carriageway
OL,9,Fbeing proposed - it is calling for a
OL,10,Fsubstantial upgrade to the road with
OL,11,Fmore overtaking lanes and bypasses
OL,12,Fbeing built as well.
OL,14,FOne of the main campaigners in support
OL,15,Fof the new dual carriageway has urged
OL,16,Fanyone thinking of objecting to the
OL,17,Fproject to "reflect on their course of
OL,18,Faction given the amount of carnage of
OL,19,Fthe road."
