OL,7,FNiall McKenna from the A5 Enough is
OL,8,FEnough campaign says the number of
OL,9,Faccidents and deaths on the road is
OL,10,F"grotesque."
OL,12,F"The on-going carnage is devastating
OL,13,Ffamilies and communities in this
OL,14,Flocale," he said.
OL,16,F"The delivery of the promise of July
OL,17,F2007 will belatedly save many lives
OL,18,Fand the carnage of this construct will
OL,19,Fbe consigned to history.
